{"id":4300,"date":"2025-06-19T15:27:30","date_gmt":"2025-06-19T08:27:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4300"},"modified":"2025-11-14T16:20:14","modified_gmt":"2025-11-14T09:20:14","slug":"kem-cham-mun-gsc-acne-clear-cream","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/kem-cham-mun-gsc-acne-clear-cream\/","title":{"rendered":"Kem Ch\u1ea5m M\u1ee5n GSC Acne Clear Cream"},"content":{"rendered":"<p data-start=\"543\" data-end=\"1053\"><em>M\u1ee5n vi\u00eam lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc, m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7, m\u1ee5n nang kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y \u0111au nh\u1ee9c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00e2m s\u1eb9o, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd. Trong v\u00f4 v\u00e0n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. <strong>Kem Ch\u1ea5m M\u1ee5n GSC Acne Clear Cream<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n nhanh ch\u00f3ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh cho c\u1ea3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u1ea5t.<\/em><\/p>\n\n<h2 data-start=\"1055\" data-end=\"1115\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-hinh-thanh-mun-viem-va-cach-dieu-tri-hieu-qua\"><\/span>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1377\">M\u1ee5n vi\u00eam h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh do s\u1ef1 t\u00edch t\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, g\u00e2y n\u00ean ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111au nh\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00e2m, s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 lan r\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4384\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4384\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4384 size-full\" title=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-1.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4384\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p data-start=\"1379\" data-end=\"1692\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f9ng l\u00fac v\u00e0o b\u1ed1n y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n bao g\u1ed3m: l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1edbp s\u1eebng, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, ti\u00eau vi\u00eam v\u00e0 di\u1ec7t khu\u1ea9n. Kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n GSC ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1745\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uu-diem-noi-bat-trong-cong-thuc-kem-cham-mun-gsc\"><\/span>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n GSC<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1747\" data-end=\"1922\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p tinh t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 sulfur v\u00e0 retinol c\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m AHA v\u00e0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1ng sinh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1924\" data-end=\"2197\">Sulfur v\u1edbi n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 1.5 ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u d\u01b0 th\u1eeba nhanh ch\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn \u1ed5 vi\u00eam nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng n\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2199\" data-end=\"2380\">Retinol \u1edf n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 0.01 ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y bong l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng, gi\u1ea3m t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, gi\u00fap m\u1ee5n mau l\u00e0nh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00e2m s\u1eb9o.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2382\" data-end=\"2530\">AHA d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng glycolic acid v\u00e0 citric acid gi\u00fap t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da v\u00e0 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2532\" data-end=\"2723\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 di\u1ebfp c\u00e1, tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0, kh\u1ed5 s\u00e2m, tr\u00e0 xanh v\u00e0 kim ng\u00e2n hoa \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1ng sinh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean gi\u00fap ti\u00eau vi\u00eam, di\u1ec7t khu\u1ea9n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"2725\" data-end=\"2784\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-vuot-troi-duoc-chung-minh-qua-phan-hoi-thuc-te\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh qua ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"2786\" data-end=\"2905\">Kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n GSC \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf qua kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng sau 9 tu\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho th\u1ea5y:<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4385\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4385\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4385\" title=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4385\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p data-start=\"2907\" data-end=\"2987\">Ch\u00edn m\u01b0\u01a1i ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam kh\u00f4 c\u1ed3i sau 24 gi\u1edd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2989\" data-end=\"3058\">T\u00e1m m\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1ed1t ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y v\u1ebft th\u00e2m m\u1edd d\u1ea7n, da s\u00e1ng l\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3060\" data-end=\"3166\">Ch\u00edn m\u01b0\u01a1i l\u0103m ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng chai m\u1ee5n hay nh\u1eddn thu\u1ed1c sau khi d\u00f9ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3168\" data-end=\"3379\">Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t m\u1ee5n nhanh ch\u00f3ng, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c t\u1eebng b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, benzoyl peroxide ho\u1eb7c kh\u00e1ng sinh m\u1ea1nh.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"3381\" data-end=\"3434\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"an-toan-tuyet-doi-voi-cong-thuc-khong-gay-kich-ung\"><\/span>An to\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3436\" data-end=\"3844\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 r\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da, kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n GSC ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, d\u1ea7u kho\u00e1ng, sulfate hay paraben. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da n\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho c\u1ea3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c da c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ea1nh.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3846\" data-end=\"4055\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng, cho ph\u00e9p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3 v\u00e0o ban ng\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, gi\u00fap thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ho\u1eb7c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"4057\" data-end=\"4100\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-su-dung-de-dat-hieu-qua-toi-uu\"><\/span>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4102\" data-end=\"4352\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o b\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong chu tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ho\u1eb7c ban ng\u00e0y. L\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5m tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, tr\u00e1nh thoa lan sang v\u00f9ng da xung quanh \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4 da.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"4354\" data-end=\"4489\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi serum d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00f9ng da xung quanh n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang bong tr\u00f3c.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4387\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4387\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4387\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-3.webp\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4387\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p data-start=\"4491\" data-end=\"4651\">Lu\u00f4n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u00e0o ban ng\u00e0y n\u1ebfu d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng. Tr\u00e1nh d\u00f9ng cho to\u00e0n m\u1eb7t ho\u1eb7c cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n hay m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"4653\" data-end=\"4749\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u00ean v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb vi\u00eam da d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, nhi\u1ec5m corticoid ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang b\u1ecb tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eb7ng.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"4751\" data-end=\"4779\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-su-dung-phu-hop\"><\/span>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4781\" data-end=\"4934\">Kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n GSC \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho l\u00e0n da b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc, m\u1ee5n m\u1ee7, m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1eady th\u00ec ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n nang.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4388\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4388\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4388\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-4.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4388\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p data-start=\"4936\" data-end=\"5069\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng cho c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n do d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng v\u00ec s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb cao v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5071\" data-end=\"5192\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang t\u00ecm gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh cho l\u00e0n da.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"5194\" data-end=\"5261\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-thuc-thanh-phan-noi-bat-ho-tro-toan-dien-trong-dieu-tri-mun\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"5263\" data-end=\"5372\">Kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n GSC l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4385\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4385\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4385\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/79-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4385\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p data-start=\"5374\" data-end=\"5457\">Sulfur n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 1.5 ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m gi\u00fap l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 nhanh nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n, kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, gi\u1ea3m b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5459\" data-end=\"5547\">Retinol 0.01 ph\u1ea7n tr\u0103m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, gi\u1ea3m s\u1eebng h\u00f3a v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u da sau m\u1ee5n.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5549\" data-end=\"5663\">AHA v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n glycolic acid v\u00e0 citric acid l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, gi\u00fap b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5665\" data-end=\"5832\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t l\u00e1 tr\u00e0 xanh, ho\u00e0ng li\u00ean nh\u1eadt, kim ng\u00e2n hoa v\u00e0 di\u1ebfp c\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ng sinh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu, ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"5834\" data-end=\"5950\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb m\u1ee7 c\u00e2y \u0111u \u0111\u1ee7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u00e2m sau m\u1ee5n.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"5952\" data-end=\"5963\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"5965\" data-end=\"6452\">Trong th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i da l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n GSC Acne Clear Cream kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 x\u1eed l\u00fd hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng. Nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m mang l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n cho l\u00e0n da \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong c\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam n\u1eb7ng ho\u1eb7c t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"6454\" data-end=\"6631\">H\u00e3y bi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tu\u00fdp kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t an to\u00e0n cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 GSC Acne Clear Cream.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Kem Ch\u1ea5m M\u1ee5n GSC Acne Clear Cream \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4389,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4300","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4300","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4300"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4300\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":6264,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4300\/revisions\/6264"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4389"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4300"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4300"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4300"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}